Package: geneGPS
Type: Package
Title: Gene-Level Pleiotropy Scores (GPS) from GWAS Summary Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Mengyao",
           family = "Liu",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "liumengyao163@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Mengyao Liu <liumengyao163@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/Lemenyeux/geneGPS/
Description: Provides a workflow for deriving gene-level pleiotropy scores
    from GWAS summary statistics. The workflow derives two scores to capture 
    different facets of gene pleiotropy, including (1) the number of trait 
    dimensions associated with a gene (referred to as the "number" score, 
    GPS-N), and (2) the overall magnitude of associations across trait 
    dimensions (referred to as "magnitude" score, GPS-M).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
